data.description: Motivated Seller!  Deep water Jones Creek offers spectacular Views, Fishing, Crabbing and Shrimping in your backyard from your private Dock and Floating Dock. House in pristine condition. Lush, blooming landscape frames this lovely home.  Covered Patio. Lovely Ceramic Tile Flooring, updated kitchen appliance, Updated Baths, Wood burning Fireplace, 3 bedrooms, Family Room, Sun Porch with 3 year old new Air Conditioning has fabulous views! Enjoy your front yard swing while watching birds and smelling the roses or relax on the waterfront and enjoy the coastal water scape!  Move in ready!  Crabbing and Shrimping from your own dock! 60 ft dock extension completed 4 years ago.  A piece  of heaven in Coastal Georgia on Historic, Unspoiled Colonel's Island. Do not buy until you see this property!
data.whatILove: Location! Location! Location!  Historic, Pristine, Coastal Paradise on Colonel's Island in Liberty County. Shrimp, Crab, Fish from Private Dock. Enjoy Deepwater and Marsh Views or linger in your lushly landscaped yard and bird watch and flower watch!
